:"2018-11-04T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"20分鐘 畫眉搞最耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f43b22bcae4420607b2babd9f596ac5ba1a19b","tid":889221,"uid":156587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80c2becbb47bd469992515af6719df5ec05a2cd3","tid":889221,"uid":213589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"唔化全妝係咪會比人鄙視㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"要睇到你嘴有化 條眉要有 眼妝要有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 化化下就全妝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n粉底除非個日真係皮膚狀況超好先可以唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個月都唔知有冇一兩日"},{"pid":"c60fc243192f873a7a1ea3bcc2c21b3c0601df8e","tid":889221,"uid":121881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"唔畫眼線就半個鐘 <br />\n畫埋要1個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07e71105edb89177cd9fff9215cef9fa25a4527","tid":889221,"uid":145779,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"點解一定要化妝？合約有寫？<br />\n<br />\n同你相反我返工唔化妝<br />\n有時化完返去仲要比人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a0474a968665d19533041a40dd5879edee220e","tid":889221,"uid":149365,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"我都覺化妝好煩 但返工又唔可以唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我手腳好慢 洗面刷牙都15分鐘<br />\n化妝前又要護膚都無左10分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n化完妝又要夾下頭 襯下衫 執下手袋 起碼9個字先出到門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2458c7626d07a68752c8950a1432babc9d20e7","tid":889221,"uid":219646,"