" />"},{"pid":"3b6251c17e2c8f1587174478d2300b133acfed5c","tid":889221,"uid":53399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"做地盤"},{"pid":"3bba244af54e56fc4c4cf66fb3f3782f7cef3af0","tid":889221,"uid":206480,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"番工嘅話只會化淡妝<br />\n粉底+眉+啡色眼影（一層）+碎粉+唇膏<br />\n<br />\n十五分鐘搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fe9d2770e400a1b4bbacd18c0df25be01c3154","tid":889221,"uid":6966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"好奇 點解你地要化咁耐？我畫埋眼線痴埋雙眼皮膠紙 假眼捷毛 查埋成塊臉， 15分鐘搞掂。不過可能我化左4年日日返工化好熟。<br />\n好奇你地邊part花最多時間"},{"pid":"20a61c0fbaa744660300bc8d1a06ca6ab701b78d","tid":889221,"uid":25857,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"快有快化慢有慢化<br />\n<br />\n快嘅話可以二十分鐘full make up 夾埋個頭<br />\n<br />\n慢慢玩可以化兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d951e69b631b816d4eaa3d709c871475ac8f84","tid":889221,"uid":25857,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"14fe9d2770e400a1b4bbacd18c0df25be01c3154","tid":889221,"uid":6966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"好奇 點解你地要化咁耐？我畫埋眼線痴埋雙眼皮膠紙 假眼捷毛 查埋成塊臉， 15分鐘搞掂。不過可能我化左4年日日返工化好熟。<br />\n好奇你地邊part花最多時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"眉毛"},{"pid":"75398a3288c0bb42dd3302d255949270f88c1ac9","tid":889221,"uid":156587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b07e71105edb89177cd9fff9215cef9fa25a4527","tid":889221,"uid":145779,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"點解一定要化妝？合約有寫？<br />\n<br />\n同你相反我返工唔化妝<br />\n有時化完返去仲要比人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018